OL,3,CFour stabbed after 'serious disorder'
OL,4,Cat train station
OL,6,FFour people have been stabbed
OL,7,Ffollowing a 'serious disorder' at
OL,8,FTenby railway station yesterday
OL,9,Fevening.
OL,11,FDyfed Powys Police confirmed officers
OL,12,Fwere called at around 9.50pm on 7
OL,13,FApril to reports of a disturbance
OL,14,Finvolving a group of youths.
OL,16,FDuring the incident, one individual
OL,17,Fwas reported to be in possession of a
OL,18,Fknife, and four youths sustained stab
OL,19,Fwounds.
