OL,3,CFour stabbed after 'serious disorder'
OL,4,Cat train station
OL,6,FPolice confirmed that all injuries are
OL,7,Fcurrently believed to be non-life-
OL,8,Fthreatening, and those affected are
OL,9,Freceiving medical treatment.
OL,11,FA 16-year-old individual and a 19-year-
OL,12,Fold man have been arrested on
OL,13,Fsuspicion of Section 18 assault. Both
OL,14,Fremain in custody while enquiries
OL,15,Fcontinue.
OL,17,FThe investigation is now being led by
OL,18,FBritish Transport Police, and police
OL,19,Fare urging anyone who witnessed the
OL,20,Fincident or has relevant information
OL,21,Fto get in touch.
