OL,3,CFour stabbed after 'serious disorder'
OL,4,Cat train station
OL,6,FAuthorities say the situation is now
OL,7,Funder control and the area has been
OL,8,Fsecured, with increased police patrols
OL,9,Fremaining in place to reassure the
OL,10,Fpublic.
OL,12,FA spokesperson from Dyfed Powys Police
OL,13,Fsaid: "Dyfed-Powys Police were called
OL,14,Fto reports of serious disorder
OL,15,Finvolving a group of youths at Tenby
OL,16,Ftrain station at approx. 9.50pm this
OL,17,Fevening (Tuesday, 7 April). During the
OL,18,Fincident, an individual was in
OL,19,Fpossession of a knife, which resulted
OL,20,Fin four youths sustaining stab wounds.
