OL,3,CFour stabbed after 'serious disorder'
OL,4,Cat train station
OL,6,F"All injuries are currently assessed
OL,7,Fas non-life threatening, and those
OL,8,Faffected are receiving appropriate
OL,9,Fmedical treatment."
OL,11,FThey added: "Officers attended the
OL,12,Fscene promptly, and a 16-year-old
OL,13,Fyouth and a 19-year-old man have been
OL,14,Farrested on suspicion of Section 18
OL,15,FAssault. They are in police custody
OL,16,Fand an investigation is underway.
OL,18,F"British Transport Police have primacy
OL,19,Ffor the incident and are leading
OL,20,Fenquiries."
